<asp:Content ID="Content1" ContentPlaceHolderID="demo" runat="Server">
    <p>
        EO.ListBox offers many enhanced features comparing to standard ListBox control. Key features include:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Supports all popular browsers: IE 6.0+, FireFox 1.0+, Mozilla 1.3+, Opera 7.2+,
            Safari 1.3+ and Chrome; </li>
        <li>Fully customizable with CSS for almost all parts: the border, frame, header, footer,
            regular item, selected items --- everything can be styled; </li>
        <li>Built-in support for header and footer; </li>
        <li>Multi-selection based on shift, alt or control key; </li>
        <li>Support icon, text and value for each item; </li>
        <li>Support "infinite list" where it dynamically loads more items as you scroll down;
        </li>
        <li>Flexible client side JavaScript interface and extensive server side interface;
        </li>
    </ul>
</asp:Content>
